This paper involves the use of deep neural networks for learning optimal spacecraft trajectories, which falls under the category of control systems (cs.SY). The use of deep learning algorithms for trajectory optimization also falls under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves the use of optimization techniques, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). Finally, the paper involves the use of neural networks to learn from data, which falls under the category of neural networks (cs.NE).
